  "instructions_to_main_agent": [
    "Simulate a mobile app feel within a browser using max-w-md mx-auto, hide browser scrollbars, and frame it nicely with a dark border/shadow.",
    "Do NOT use generic blue or white themes. Stick strictly to the #0A0A0A and #D4AF37 Golden Black palette.",
    "Use framer-motion to implement the 'add to cart' floating animation. The image of the dish should duplicate, scale down, and animate towards the top right cart icon.",
    "The 3 main CTAs (Dine In, Takeaway, Delivery) should be prominent below the hero banner. Give them a nice glassy gold trim.",
    "Hamburger menu should slide in from the left, containing Profile, Orders, Addresses, Offers, Payments, and Help links.",
    "Use mock data for everything. No backend required. Implement simple state for the cart.",
    "All interactive elements must have a data-testid for automated testing.",
    "Chef's Special and Customer Reviews should be implemented as horizontally scrolling flex containers (snap-x).",
    "Menu Page: Display a grid of categories. Tapping one should animate to a list of dishes for that category."
  ]
}

